metadata.name: Nature's Desire
metadata.description:
One sunray can illuminate the whole nature. Sunrays must be the sun's way of dancing to touch the surface of different mediums to nourish the art in nature itself.

"A lake so vibrant in color that it looks like a fine art painting" ~ Stefanie Payne

"He who has no dreams, let him go to a beautiful forest to have many" ~ Mehmet Murat Ildan
